{"tid":2115461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國逾3千人鄉郊區參與狂野派對　警方指主辦者自私","createTime":"2020-07-19T13:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T02:37:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d0ba0e6df4bd523d951773504f8ef62d0c4403","tid":2115461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538699-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538699-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8psIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=db7b4b98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538699-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d1ed2a50\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538699-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國超過3000人在南部城市巴斯的鄉郊地區，通宵參與狂野派對。警方批評主辦者在新型肺炎疫情之下舉行派對是自私行為，強調會對違法者採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n派對在當地星期六晚開始，附近城市都有人投訴聲浪太大，令他們難以入睡。<br />\n<br />\n警方說在當地周末晚11時左右開始接報，派人到場巡邏，發現幾百人在場，有更多人持續前來參與，即使封閉行車線，亦有人棄車徒步前往。警方到周日上午近7時，仍要趕走前來的車輛。<br />\n<br />\n警方解釋未有終止狂野派對，是因為經評估後認為，在黑暗及潮濕的環境中，強行介入一個有超過3000人參與的活動，會對公眾安全構成威脅。"},{"pid":"434b5166c44153654c3f560cbfe0510b98722316","tid":2115461,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"又係武肺party?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77bad992b3b759210c5f7c759124f3b4655d956","tid":2115461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"434b5166c44153654c3f560cbfe0510b98722316","tid":2115461,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"又係武肺party?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fc385e92ff408030be505a1f933ce35f59d1fe","tid":2115461,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"全名係咪叫瘋狂扑野派對"}]}